title: Hillary Clinton
deleted: On January 20, 2021, the Clintons attended the [[inauguration of Joe Biden]], alongside [[George W. Bush]], [[Laura Bush]], [[Barack Obama]] and [[Michelle Obama]].

On September 11, 2021, the Clintons attended a 9/11 memorial to commemorate the 20th anniversary of the attacks.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Biden, Obama and Clinton mark 9/11 in New York with display of unity|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-obama-clinton-911-new-york-display-of-unity/|access-date=2021-09-11|website=www.cbsnews.com|language=en-US}}</ref>

title: Hillary Clinton
deleted: In 2018, a false rumor circling around the internet called “frazzledrip,” or frazzled.rip, claimed that a video of Hillary and [[Huma Abedin]] [[Rape|raped]], tortured, [[Skinning|ripped the face off]], killed, and drank the blood of a young girl for a satanic ritual. The false video was allegedly found on [[Anthony Weiner]]’s laptop, prior to his arrest in 2017. The video is closely connected to [[Pizzagate conspiracy theory|PizzaGate]] and [[QAnon]].
